  "aiHints": {
    "analysisContext": "SKP binary: offset 0='SketchUp Model'(14B), offset 14=0x00(null), offset 15=format_version(uint32 LE). After header: tag-length-value binary encoding for older versions (<=16) or Protobuf-based for v17+. Key data: geometry chunks (vertices as float64 triplets, edges as vertex index pairs, faces as polygon with coplanar normals), material definitions (color RGBA + optional texture), layer/tag table, scene (named view) list, entity attributes (dictionary key=value). Embedded textures: BMP or PNG data inline in material records. SKP is NOT publicly documented; SketchUp C API (SDK) is the only official reader. Community: LibreSketchUp reverse-engineered v3-v8 structure.",
    "suggestedInspections": [
      "Bytes 0-13: 'SketchUp Model' ASCII magic — confirms SKP format",
      "Bytes 15-18 (uint32 LE): format version (3-23 → SketchUp 3 to 2023)",
      "After header: binary TLV or Protobuf records (v17+ uses Protobuf encoding)",
      "Search for PNG/BMP magic within file body for embedded texture thumbnails"
    ]
  },
  "software": [
