  "formatRelationships": {
    "category": "CAD",
    "extensions": [".skp"],
    "relatedFormats": ["DXF", "STEP", "OBJ", "COLLADA", "3DS"],
    "note": "SKP is Trimble's proprietary format for SketchUp. SketchUp can export to DXF, DWG, STEP, OBJ, COLLADA, FBX, and IFC. The SKP format is version-incompatible (newer SketchUp cannot open very old SKP files and vice versa without conversion). SketchUp C API SDK provides licensed C++ read/write support."
  },
